CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 10, 1970, pg. 15, reads: "Frogs Dinner - Dancing Party Sparks Holiday Season - The Christmas Tree - gets the attention of lovely Margaret French and her fiance, Dr. Ralph Rivere. The two will be married around Easter. All Courier Photos by 'Teenie' Harris."
TitMainTitle: Margaret French and Dr. Ralph Rivere, posed next to Christmas tree in Redwood Motor Hotel for FROGS Dinner - Dance party
